Blog
=====================================

This is sample application for simple Blog. Where is demostrated Play 2.2, Bootstrap and AngularJS.

- Play 2.2.1
- Bootstrap
- AngularJS


Install MongoDb on OSX

for OSX use homebrew
brew update
brew install mongodb
mondodb
mongod

check full installation guide http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/tutorial/install-mongodb-on-os-x/
